### info

`planter info <name>`

Prints all info about a planter in your list.

**Args**

`<name>`

Name of the planter to show info for.

**Examples**

```bash
# Usage
planter info my-planter

# Output
Name:             my-planter
Location:         user/repo-name
Type:             Remote
Pinned:           1
Date Added:       Aug 24, 2022 7:40:08 PM
```

